                
                SERVER CREATION OF E-COMMERCE



1.create package.json file- npm init
2.Create node modules -Install epress - npm i express
3. create index.js  (Main Entry Point)
4.In index.js
            i)import express
            ii) create an application using express
            iii) setup a port number
            iv)use json parser for server response
5.integration -  (connecting backend and front end)
         i)Install cors -npm i cors
         ii)Import cos into index.js)
         iii)using cors specify the origin to the server
               origin:('http://localhost:4200')
 6.Services -create a folder service
           1. dataservices.js
           1. db.js
  7. backend and mongo db connection
